# Making flowcharts

*Click on this presentation and press 'f' for full screen.*



We use [app.diagrams.net](https://app.diagrams.net/) to
make our flowcharts.

The easiest way to get going is to start with one of
the example flowcharts. If you click on one,
it'll zoom in, and there will be a pencil
button <i class="fas fa-pencil-alt"></i>
you can click on to edit your own copy.



You can copy existing objects with <kbd>Ctrl</kbd>+drag.

